nodes.name: PutBacklogTag
nodes.notes: Add "backlog" tag. FreeScout should then change the ticket's status to "pending"

json.name: Re: [freescout-helpdesk/freescout] Translation ignored for search criteria (Issue #3058)
json.text_content:
Joshua Wowk | Sys Admin | HPNE | 401-349-5153

Click here to book time with me

From: Commander Keen notifications@github.comSent: Tuesday, May 30, 2023 7:26 AMTo: freescout-helpdesk/freescout freescout@noreply.github.comCc: Subscribed subscribed@noreply.github.comSubject: [freescout-helpdesk/freescout] Translation ignored for search criteria (Issue #3058) 

Hello.

It seems the translation is ignored for the search criteria



After some tests, I noted the translation exists in the language file but the given keys in the search form are lower cased and so they don't match.

Example

does not match (capital A)

{ "Assigned": "Zugewiesen" }

matches

{ "assigned": "Zugewiesen" }

Same issue exists with modules like the tag module

NOT RELATED

It seems there is a contentual mistake in the german translation

On this line, conversation is tranlslated into notes

https://github.com/freescout-helpdesk/freescout/blob/ee2269fdf1db5693676df82064818dee366638f5/resources/lang/de.json#L710

Correct translation should be

Benutzer sind berechtigt Gespräche zu löschen

Thanks in advance

—Reply to this email directly, view it on GitHub, or unsubscribe.You are receiving this because you are subscribed to this thread.Message ID: freescout-helpdesk/freescout/issues/3058@github.com
